{"tid":1379144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又有聯署］反對警方反對成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:22:40.000Z","uid":264683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"153e8e5038987bc787280dcbb8276f5ac706b023","tid":1379144,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:48:47.000Z","msg":"Hello, 我針對警方7月24號，致林女士的信，寫左4點回應，反對警方反對成立獨立調查委員會。因為係長文，我廢事喺到po，入到去睇唔睇都好，<br />\n麻煩各位巴絲幫手簽左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/hong-kong-government-反對警方反對成立獨立調查委員會/exp/cl_/bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-gb/v2/904619756?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-gb%3Av2&amp;recruited_by_id=3d390380-cc40-11e8-994b-e5a703bdc21c&amp;recruiter=904619756&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=tap_basic_share&amp;utm_term=e0a9ac60ee6247c7a4ffe04b91bd8be8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fhong-kong-government-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%2Fexp%2Fcl_%2Fbandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-gb%2Fv2%2F904619756%3Futm_content%3Dbandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-gb%253Av2%26recruited_by_id%3D3d390380-cc40-11e8-994b-e5a703bdc21c%26recruiter%3D904619756%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dtap_basic_share%26utm_term%3De0a9ac60ee6247c7a4ffe04b91bd8be8&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=dcf7bf1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/hong-kong-government-反對警方反對成立獨立調查委員會/exp/cl_/bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-gb/v2/904619756?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-gb%3Av2&amp;recruited_by_id=3d390380-cc40-11e8-994b-e5a703bdc21c&amp;recruiter=904619756&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=tap_basic_share&amp;utm_term=e0a9ac60ee6247c7a4ffe04b91bd8be8</a><br />\n<br />\n眼見呢兩日黑警暴力行為不斷升級<br />\n而黑警仍不知廉恥反對獨立調查<br />\n我地要用硬實力升級對抗至餘，亦要用軟實力<br />\n而家就要量化民意<br />\n一黎用數量話比警察政府知，香港人堅決反對你地反對獨立調查委員會<br />\n二黎可以日後交比相關議員作籌碼<br />\n<br />\n再加上各方壓力<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一定要逼到政府成立獨立調查委員會</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>呢樣係最低消費</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f129dee8557d01304d270dde2535d53a554d7261","tid":1379144,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:50:37.000Z","msg":"推 清算黑警惡行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09eed7bc285497f3e9306da6c84924165f1ed36","tid":1379144,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:53:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fac264202c1b489c740b98a6c28747dce80286d","tid":1379144,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:55:27.000Z","msg":"個標題雙重否定好似有D亂, 要LOAD一LOAD先明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f76a9792eec21035431fc44e71da21794433fea","tid":1379144,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f904e766e9f93497fdf337a8ddf3bb10531b68c","tid":1379144,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:03:50.000Z","msg":"警方反對成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n我地反對佢哋立場<br />\n所以係反對警方反對xxxxx<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2330684ee3ecc6c8193502c30d4b48739c334e07","tid":1379144,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e03d6f667c99f7bc8f3fa011d9ff66c847b7d6c9","tid":1379144,"uid":264683,"like